.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
.TH ecd-check 1  "check " 
.SH NAME
ecd\-check \- Detect file encoding(s)
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBecd check\fR [\fB\-f\fR|\fB\-\-file\fR] [\fB\-d\fR|\fB\-\-dir\fR] [\fB\-p\fR|\fB\-\-pattern\fR] [\fB\-i\fR|\fB\-\-ignore\fR] [\fB\-e\fR|\fB\-\-exclude\fR] [\fB\-\-no\-default\-excludes\fR] [\fB\-j\fR|\fB\-\-jobs\fR] [\fB\-v\fR|\fB\-\-verbose\fR] [\fB\-q\fR|\fB\-\-quiet\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Detect file encoding(s)
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-f\fR, \fB\-\-file\fR \fI<PATH>\fR
File(s) to check (repeatable)
.TP
\fB\-d\fR, \fB\-\-dir\fR \fI<PATH>\fR
Directory/directories to scan recursively (repeatable)
.TP
\fB\-p\fR, \fB\-\-pattern\fR \fI<PATTERN>\fR [default: **/*]
Glob pattern to filter files when scanning directories
.TP
\fB\-i\fR, \fB\-\-ignore\fR \fI<ENC>\fR
Ignore files with this encoding (case\-insensitive)
.TP
\fB\-e\fR, \fB\-\-exclude\fR \fI<NAME>\fR
Additional directory names to exclude
.TP
\fB\-\-no\-default\-excludes\fR
Disable default directory excludes (.git, node_modules, target)
.TP
\fB\-j\fR, \fB\-\-jobs\fR \fI<N>\fR
Number of parallel jobs
.TP
\fB\-v\fR, \fB\-\-verbose\fR
Print statistics to stderr
.TP
\fB\-q\fR, \fB\-\-quiet\fR
Suppress normal output (errors only)
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
